      <div class="text-center">
      <img class="img-fluid ml-5" src=https://dimidium.com.ec/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/INSUMOS.png alt="">
<center>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-clipboard2-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
